sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as 관리자
    participant UI as React UI (Resources)
    participant Page as React UI (NewResource /resources/new)
    participant Preload as electronAPI
    participant IPC as IPC Main (setupIpcHandlers)
    participant UC as AppUseCases
    participant Repo as PrismaResourceRepository
    participant DB as SQLite DB

    Admin->>UI: '+ 자원 추가' 버튼 클릭
    activate UI
    UI->>Page: navigate('/resources/new')
    deactivate UI
    activate Page
    Page-->>Admin: 자원 등록 페이지 렌더링

    Admin->>Page: 자원명, 카테고리, 상태, 설명 입력
    opt 사용자 정의 컬럼 추가 (Extension Point)
        Admin->>Page: '+ 컬럼 추가' 클릭 → 속성명/값 입력
    end

    Admin->>Page: '등록하기' 버튼 클릭
    Note over Page: customFields 배열을 JSON.stringify()로 직렬화
    Page->>Preload: invoke('resource:create', { name, categoryId, status, customFields })
    activate Preload
    Preload->>IPC: IPC 채널 전송
    activate IPC
    IPC->>UC: resource.create({ name, categoryId, status, customFields })
    activate UC
    UC->>Repo: create({ name, categoryId, status, customFields })
    activate Repo
    Repo->>DB: prisma.resource.create({ data })
    activate DB
    DB-->>Repo: 생성된 Resource 레코드 반환
    deactivate DB
    Repo-->>UC: Resource 반환
    deactivate Repo
    UC-->>IPC: 결과 반환
    deactivate UC
    IPC-->>Preload: { success: true, data }
    deactivate IPC
    Preload-->>Page: Promise Resolve
    deactivate Preload
    Page->>Page: navigate('/resources')
    deactivate Page
    Note over Page: 자원 목록 페이지로 자동 복귀
